AnimatedProgressBar from Firefox Focus
======================================

This is the original source code of the AnimatedProgressBar from Firefox Focus,
packaged as a standalone Android Library project to comply with the terms of 
the Mozilla Public License 2.0.

Any changes/improvements to these files will be made available in source code 
form in this repository, as required by the MPL.

Source from this repository can be reused in other projects, even in 
closed-source commercial projects, as long as any modifications made to the 
files in this repository are also made available.

